item.title: CVE-2017-20128|2024-08-05T21:45:26.204Z -- unspecified -- kb%20messages%20php%20script
item.description: A vulnerability has been found in KB Messages PHP Script 1.0 and classified as critical. Affected by this vulnerability is an unknown functionality. The manipulation of the argument username/password with the input 'or''=' leads to sql injection. The attack can be launched remotely. The exploit has been disclosed to the public and may be used.
